    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Great opportunity here \u2014 this is a solid, dependable vehicle in good condition! It shows normal signs of everyday use but has been well cared for overall, with no major mechanical concerns and a presentable appearance inside and out. It drives comfortably and reliably, making it a smart choice for anyone looking for a trustworthy daily driver without the premium price of a mint-condition car. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be pleasantly impressed!",
      "price": 35000.0,
